Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:14.38,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}你所萌生的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.38,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}定是正确无误之志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:20.01,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}我们怀着同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:24.22,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:27.51,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.27,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:34.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:40.19,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:44.82,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:52.29,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:57.79,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:01.09,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:02.92,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:12.02,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:14.56,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}为我们指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:21.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}{\fad(0,800)}梦想必亲手实现
